{"id":73567,"date":"2023-07-13T07:30:26","date_gmt":"2023-07-13T12:30:26","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/?p=73567"},"modified":"2023-07-27T11:52:13","modified_gmt":"2023-07-27T16:52:13","slug":"the-complete-guide-to-spotify-advertising-tune-into-success","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/ws\/2023\/07\/13\/spotify-advertising","title":{"rendered":"The Complete Guide to Spotify Advertising: Tune Into Success!"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>The \u201cTikTok made me buy it\u201d era is over.<\/p>\n<p>Well, not quite, but it isn\u2019t the only platform where users sincerely engage with sponsored content\u2014Spotify is a close second (and may be gunning for the top place).<\/p>\n<p>The second volume of <a href=\"https:\/\/ads.spotify.com\/en-US\/sonic-science\/vol-2\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Sonic Science<\/a>, a biometric study that reveals the impact of digital audio and ad engagement, found that Spotify listeners remember the brands they hear about on podcasts or while streaming music.<\/p>\n<p>And ad recall isn\u2019t the only metric that\u2019s through the roof.<\/p>\n<p>1 in 5 study participants reported looking up a brand or product after hearing about it in a Spotify ad, and 30% said they\u2019re likely to make a purchase\u2014nothing but great news for advertisers looking to get into audio advertising.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-homepage-example.jpg\" alt=\"spotify advertising example on homepage - desktop and mobile\" width=\"817\" height=\"524\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-73575\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-homepage-example.jpg 817w, https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-homepage-example-480x308.jpg 480w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 817px, 100vw\" \/><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em><a href=\"https:\/\/www.adweek.com\/performance-marketing\/spotify-launches-display-ads-guarantee-viewability-170330\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Source<\/a><\/em><\/p>\n<p>But planning is more important than execution in the long run. So before you jet off to create your first Spotify ad, here\u2019s (almost) everything you need to know about how Spotify advertising works, if it\u2019s worth investing in, and how to create some sonic serendipity.<\/p>\n<div class='et-box et-shadow'>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class='et-box-content'><h3>Table of contents<\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#definition\">What is Spotify advertising? (+placements)<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"#benefits\">Benefits of Spotify advertising<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"#howto\">How to advertise on Spotify<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"#tips\">Best practices for Spotify advertising<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"#cost\">Spotify advertising costs<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"#reporting\">Measuring the impact of ads<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"#examples\">Real-life examples of Spotify ads<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"#faqs\">FAQs<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul><\/div><\/div>\n<div id=\"definition\"><\/div>\n<h2>What is Spotify advertising?<\/h2>\n<p>Spotify advertising includes running audio ads (accompanied by a branded video or image) between songs, podcasts, and playlists, typically within the free version of Spotify.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-main-placement-example.jpg\" alt=\"spotify advertising main placement example \" width=\"328\" height=\"598\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-73576\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-main-placement-example.jpg 328w, https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-main-placement-example-165x300.jpg 165w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 328px) 100vw, 328px\" \/><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em><a href=\"https:\/\/ads.spotify.com\/en-US\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Source<\/a><\/em><\/p>\n<h3>Other Spotify ad types<\/h3>\n<p>Aside from the typical Spotify ads mentioned above, there are a few custom options available for Spotify advertising. These vary in costs and cannot be run as part of the self-serve ad platform (we&#8217;ll get more into that later).<\/p>\n<h4>Sponsored Playlist<\/h4>\n<p>With <a href=\"https:\/\/ads.spotify.com\/en-US\/ad-experiences\/sponsored-playlist-ad-specs\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Sponsored Playlists<\/a>, you can run your ads when people listen to Spotify\u2019s most popular owned and operated playlists. Spotify\u2019s streaming intelligence can help you better <a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/ws\/2022\/05\/11\/target-audience\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">understand your target audience<\/a> and identify the best playlists that align with your brand.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-sponsored-playlist.jpg\" alt=\"spotify advertising - example of sponsored playlist\" width=\"789\" height=\"600\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-73578\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-sponsored-playlist.jpg 789w, https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-sponsored-playlist-480x365.jpg 480w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 789px, 100vw\" \/><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em><a href=\"https:\/\/localiq.com\/blog\/ai-for-email-marketing\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Source<\/a><\/em><\/p>\n<h4>Overlay<\/h4>\n<p>When listeners first open the Spotify app or return to it, they\u2019re greeted with the <a href=\"https:\/\/ads.spotify.com\/en-US\/ad-experiences\/display-ads-specs\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Overlay<\/a>\u2014an ad engineered for viewability that ensures significant brand impact. This ad is clickable and can be used to <a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/ws\/2014\/08\/14\/increase-traffic-to-my-website\">drive traffic<\/a> back to your site or app.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-overlay-ad.jpg\" alt=\"spotify advertising - overlay ad placement example\" width=\"782\" height=\"600\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-73579\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-overlay-ad.jpg 782w, https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-overlay-ad-480x368.jpg 480w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 782px, 100vw\" \/><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em><a href=\"https:\/\/ads.spotify.com\/en-US\/ad-experiences\/display-ads-specs\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Source<\/a><\/em><\/p>\n<h4>Homepage Takeover<\/h4>\n<p>Take over Spotify\u2019s desktop homepage for 24 hours with the <a href=\"https:\/\/ads.spotify.com\/en-US\/ad-experiences\/homepage-takeover-specs\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Homepage Takeover<\/a>. This clickable ad supports rich media that allows you to add interactive elements.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-homepage-takeover.jpg\" alt=\"spotify advertising - homepage takeover ad example\" width=\"784\" height=\"599\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-73580\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-homepage-takeover.jpg 784w, https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-homepage-takeover-480x367.jpg 480w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 784px, 100vw\" \/><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em><a href=\"https:\/\/ads.spotify.com\/en-US\/ad-experiences\/homepage-takeover-specs\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Source<\/a><\/em><\/p>\n<h4>Leaderboard<\/h4>\n<p>When Spotify is in view, you can showcase a visual ad which will be the only message for 30 seconds. This clickable <a href=\"https:\/\/ads.spotify.com\/en-US\/ad-experiences\/leaderboard-specs\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Leaderboard<\/a> ad can help you expand your reach.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-leaderboard.jpg\" alt=\"spotify advertising - leaderboard ad placement example\" width=\"787\" height=\"598\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-73581\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-leaderboard.jpg 787w, https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-leaderboard-480x365.jpg 480w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 787px, 100vw\" \/><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em><a href=\"https:\/\/ads.spotify.com\/en-US\/ad-experiences\/leaderboard-specs\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Source<\/a><\/em><\/p>\n<div id=\"benefits\"><\/div>\n<h2>Is Spotify good for advertising?<\/h2>\n<p>Short answer: Heck yes, it is!<\/p>\n<p>Digital audio is a sound investment (get it?). And with the recent surge in demand for both podcasts and music (thanks to the numerous lockdowns and quarantines), advertisers have been flocking to the medium.<\/p>\n<p>And Spotify is sitting pretty at the top with the largest <a href=\"https:\/\/www.statista.com\/outlook\/amo\/advertising\/audio-advertising\/digital-audio-advertising\/worldwide#key-players\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">market share<\/a>.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-market-share.jpg\" alt=\"spotify advertising - market share for different audio advertising channels\" width=\"800\" height=\"599\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-73582\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-market-share.jpg 800w, https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-market-share-480x359.jpg 480w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 800px, 100vw\" \/><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em><a href=\"https:\/\/www.statista.com\/outlook\/amo\/advertising\/audio-advertising\/digital-audio-advertising\/worldwide#key-players\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Source<\/a><\/em><\/p>\n<p>Spotify offers a deeply personalized and interactive user experience, making it far more engaging, emotionally arousing, and memorable when compared to other mediums like digital video, social media, and TV.<\/p>\n<p>Here are some reasons Spotify advertising works.<\/p>\n<h3>People pay attention to Spotify ads<\/h3>\n<p>In a digital world where user attention is becoming a scarce commodity, Spotify is one of the best places to find an engaged and attentive audience.<\/p>\n<p>Dentsu International\u2019s research project, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.dentsu.com\/uk\/en\/our-latest-thinking\/unlocking-the-new-currency-of-attention\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Attention Economy<\/a>, can confirm that. Compared to the platform average, Spotify\u2019s audio ads and video ads drove +14% and +155% \u201c<a href=\"https:\/\/ads.spotify.com\/en-US\/news-and-insights\/dentsu-research-attention-economy\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">greater attentive seconds<\/a>\u201d respectively.<\/p>\n<p>Attention isn\u2019t just a nice-to-have metric\u2014it can boost ad recall and purchase intent. And the data from the Sonic Science study has already established how Spotify ads positively impact those metrics.<\/p>\n<h3>That attention and engagement lasts all day, every day<\/h3>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/ads.spotify.com\/en-US\/sonic-science\/vol-2\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">63%<\/a> of Spotify listeners stated that Spotify is an integral part of their day.<\/p>\n<p>Studies have shown that global audiences listen to <a href=\"https:\/\/www.ifpi.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/Engaging-with-Music-2022_full-report-1.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">20 hours<\/a> of music every week, and <a href=\"https:\/\/www.insiderintelligence.com\/insights\/the-podcast-industry-report-statistics\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">1 in 5 people<\/a> tune into podcasts, and that number is rapidly growing (here\u2019s looking at you true crime fans!)<\/p>\n<p>And Spotify isn\u2019t white noise\u2014listeners choose audio over screens when they either can\u2019t or don\u2019t want to engage with TV, games, or movies.<\/p>\n<p>Whether folks are cooking up a storm or tackling an important work task, they engage with the audio. That means advertisers have unparalleled access to a leaned-in audience throughout the day as opposed to other channels that serve as distractions for a limited amount of time.<\/p>\n<h3>Ad-supported subscriber base is growing<\/h3>\n<p>In Q1 2023, Spotify hit <a href=\"https:\/\/www.statista.com\/statistics\/813787\/spotify-ad-supported-monthly-active-users\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">317 million<\/a> ad-supported monthly active users\u2014a sharp increase from 295 million last year. With the streaming platform constantly adding new users to its ad-supported subscriber base, the audience of engaged listeners continues to grow.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-subscriber-growth.jpg\" alt=\"spotify advertising - subscriber growth\" width=\"936\" height=\"600\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-73583\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-subscriber-growth.jpg 936w, https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-subscriber-growth-480x308.jpg 480w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 936px, 100vw\" \/><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em><a href=\"https:\/\/www.statista.com\/statistics\/813787\/spotify-ad-supported-monthly-active-users\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Source<\/a><\/em><\/p>\n<h3>You have the chance to connect with younger listeners<\/h3>\n<p>Spotify\u2019s recently launched \u201c<a href=\"https:\/\/newsroom.spotify.com\/2023-04-13\/spotifys-new-publishing-tool-makes-it-easy-to-turn-broadcasts-into-podcasts\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Broadcast-to-Podcast<\/a>\u201d publishing tool makes it easy for radio broadcasters to turn existing content into on-demand podcasts. That means publishers can reach the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.edisonresearch.com\/weekly-insights-11-30-22-am-fm-over-the-air-vs-streaming\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">newer generations turning to digital radio<\/a> and advertisers can target more audiences on and off Spotify.<\/p>\n<h3>Spotify offers more than digital audio<\/h3>\n<p>Digital audio ads are great\u2014we just established that. But capturing attention requires a multi-format play. And that\u2019s perhaps one of the reasons why Spotify\u2019s leading the pack in Dentsu\u2019s Attention Economy study.<\/p>\n<p>Spotify\u2019s research has shown that combining audio and video ads has a significant brand impact. In fact, multiformat campaigns have a 90% increase in ad recall and more than double (<a href=\"https:\/\/www.nielsen.com\/news-center\/2018\/nielsens-relationship-spotify-continues-grow-brand-effect-measurement\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">2.2X<\/a>) brand awareness.<\/p>\n<h3>Spotify is constantly expanding its product offering<\/h3>\n<p>From new dynamic ad formats to new ways to track ad performance, Spotify is constantly developing its offering for global advertisers.<\/p>\n<p>For instance, the platform launched <a href=\"https:\/\/ads.spotify.com\/en-US\/ad-experiences\/podcast-ads-specs\/\">CTA cards for podcasts<\/a> in the US, increasing the number of places where listeners can click on them during and after an audio ad. This feature has boosted traffic to advertiser-specified URLs.<\/p>\n<h3>Sonic branding might be the next big thing<\/h3>\n<p>Although used <a href=\"https:\/\/www.ipsos.com\/sites\/default\/files\/2022-03\/power-of-you-ipsos.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">less than 10%<\/a> of the time, brand assets that use sonic brand cues are more effective than other music or roping in celebrities.<\/p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" lang=\"en\">The Netflix &#8220;ta-dum&#8221; soundmark is one of the all time greats, but doesn&#8217;t work as well in a theater because it&#8217;s only 3 seconds long.<\/p>\n<p>So Netflix commissioned Hans Zimmer to extend it for theaters and &#8230; it&#8217;s &#8230; so &#8230; good.<a href=\"https:\/\/t.co\/RGw26vCAGY\">pic.twitter.com\/RGw26vCAGY<\/a><\/p>\n<p>\u2014 Siqi Chen (@blader) <a href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/blader\/status\/1292592128086822912?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">August 9, 2020<\/a><\/p><\/blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https:\/\/platform.twitter.com\/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"><\/script><\/p>\n<p>Think about the tu-dum sound you hear when you load Netflix\u2014that\u2019s a great example of what a solid sonic identity can do for a brand. When that 3 second long sound didn\u2019t work for theaters, they had Hans Zimmer create an <a href=\"https:\/\/www.theverge.com\/2020\/8\/13\/21366371\/netflix-sound-hans-zimmer-theaters-tadum-twenty-thousand-hertz-podcast-sound-design\">extended version<\/a>.<\/p>\n<p>Cadbury followed suit by having Guy Farley <a href=\"https:\/\/www.thedrum.com\/news\/2022\/08\/16\/it-was-mad-men-pitch-scene-guy-farley-composing-cadbury-s-new-sonic-logo\">drum up a sonic logo<\/a> that captured the brand.<\/p>\n<p>While traditional jingles may be losing their appeal, there\u2019s no denying that they worked.<\/p>\n<p>And with brands trying to create a consistent <a href=\"https:\/\/localiq.com\/blog\/what-is-multichannel-marketing\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">multi-channel presence<\/a> across social media, TV, streaming, and radio, sonic branding might be the new jingle.<\/p>\n<div id=\"howto\"><\/div>\n<h2>How to advertise on Spotify<\/h2>\n<p>With Spotify Ad Studio, you can create an audio or a video (horizontal or vertical) ad.<\/p>\n<p>Here\u2019s how to use the self-serve ad manager, Spotify Ad Studio, to create an audio or video ad.<\/p>\n<h3>Step 1: Create an account (if you have one already, skip this step)<\/h3>\n<p>Make a <a href=\"https:\/\/www.spotify.com\/us\/signup\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">free Spotify account<\/a>. Use Google, Facebook, or your email to sign up.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-setup-create-account.jpg\" alt=\"spotify advertising - how to run spotify ads - create account homepage\" width=\"497\" height=\"600\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-73584\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-setup-create-account.jpg 497w, https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-setup-create-account-480x579.jpg 480w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 497px, 100vw\" \/><\/p>\n<p>Once you\u2019ve logged in, you will be able to access the <a href=\"https:\/\/ads.spotify.com\/en-US\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Ad Studio<\/a>, which will allow you to create individual ads or complex campaigns that involve ad sets.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-ad-studio-campaigns.jpg\" alt=\"spotify advertising - how to run spotify ads - campaigns page\" width=\"936\" height=\"549\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-73585\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-ad-studio-campaigns.jpg 936w, https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-ad-studio-campaigns-480x282.jpg 480w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 936px, 100vw\" \/><\/p>\n<h3>Step 2: Add campaign details<\/h3>\n<p>Name your campaign and tell Spotify what you\u2019re advertising.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-setup-new-campaign.jpg\" alt=\"spotify advertising - how to run spotify ads - create campaign name\" width=\"936\" height=\"556\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-73586\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-setup-new-campaign.jpg 936w, https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-setup-new-campaign-480x285.jpg 480w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 936px, 100vw\" \/><\/p>\n<p>Fill in the ad set name and declare an ad category (the ad category helps Spotify deliver relevant ads to listeners).<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-ad-set-details.jpg\" alt=\"spotify advertising - how to run spotify ads - enter ad set details\" width=\"936\" height=\"534\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-73587\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-ad-set-details.jpg 936w, https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-ad-set-details-480x274.jpg 480w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 936px, 100vw\" \/><\/p>\n<h3>Step 3: Set your target audience<\/h3>\n<p>Select the right location(s). You can choose specific regions or countries.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-setup-audiences.jpg\" alt=\"spotify advertising - how to run spotify ads - specify audience\" width=\"936\" height=\"548\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-73588\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-setup-audiences.jpg 936w, https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-setup-audiences-480x281.jpg 480w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 936px, 100vw\" \/><\/p>\n<p>If you\u2019re running a nationwide campaign, you can also add postal codes in bulk (up to 1,000 locations) by typing or copying and pasting them.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-setup-add-postal-codes.jpg\" alt=\"spotify advertising - how to run spotify ads - batch enter postal codes\" width=\"520\" height=\"600\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-73589\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-setup-add-postal-codes.jpg 520w, https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-setup-add-postal-codes-480x554.jpg 480w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 520px, 100vw\" \/><\/p>\n<p>Choose the age group(s) and gender(s) you want to target.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-setup-age-gender.jpg\" alt=\"spotify advertising - how to run spotify ads - choose age and gender of audience\" width=\"936\" height=\"500\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-73590\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-setup-age-gender.jpg 936w, https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-setup-age-gender-480x256.jpg 480w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 936px, 100vw\" \/><\/p>\n<p>Narrow down the interests and behaviors of your audience.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-setup-interests-behaviors.jpg\" alt=\"spotify advertising - how to run spotify ads - include interests and behaviors\" width=\"936\" height=\"580\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-73591\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-setup-interests-behaviors.jpg 936w, https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-setup-interests-behaviors-480x297.jpg 480w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 936px, 100vw\" \/><\/p>\n<p>If you select no additional targeting, you will be able to reach the broadest audience. Selecting one of the other options will help you serve your ad to a more relevant segment. For instance, if you choose contextual playlists, your ad will only be played during specific activities when listeners play a themed playlist.<\/p>\n<p>Next, choose the language you want to target.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-setup-language.jpg\" alt=\"spotify advertising - how to run spotify ads - choose language for ads\" width=\"936\" height=\"274\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-73592\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-setup-language.jpg 936w, https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-setup-language-480x141.jpg 480w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 936px, 100vw\" \/><\/p>\n<p>Select the platform(s) where you want to serve your ad.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-setup-platforms.jpg\" alt=\"spotify advertising - how to run spotify ads - choose platform for ads\" width=\"936\" height=\"241\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-73593\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-setup-platforms.jpg 936w, https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-setup-platforms-480x124.jpg 480w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 936px, 100vw\" \/><\/p>\n<h3>Step 4: Choose the format and placement of the ad<\/h3>\n<p>You have three formats to choose from: audio, horizontal, and vertical video. While Spotify recommends you choose the automatic placement, i.e., your ad will run across music and podcasts, you can opt to place your ad in music streams only.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-setup-format-placement.jpg\" alt=\"spotify advertising - how to run spotify ads - specify format and placement of ad\" width=\"936\" height=\"465\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-73594\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-setup-format-placement.jpg 936w, https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-setup-format-placement-480x238.jpg 480w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 936px, 100vw\" \/><\/p>\n<p>You also have control over whether you want to exclude your ads from playing during certain podcast episodes that may not align with your brand. Similarly, you can add topics that make sense for your brand values and offer <a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/ws\/2017\/02\/06\/personalized-marketing\">personalized experiences<\/a> to listeners.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-setup-podcast-episode-topics.jpg\" alt=\"spotify advertising - how to run spotify ads - choose any podcast content controls\" width=\"602\" height=\"598\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-73595\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-setup-podcast-episode-topics.jpg 602w, https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-setup-podcast-episode-topics-480x477.jpg 480w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 602px, 100vw\" \/><\/p>\n<h3>Step 5: Create the ad schedule and set the budget<\/h3>\n<p>You can choose to run the ad indefinitely or select a start and end date and time.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-setup-schedule-ad.jpg\" alt=\"spotify advertising - how to run spotify ads - schedule ad \" width=\"936\" height=\"417\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-73596\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-setup-schedule-ad.jpg 936w, https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-setup-schedule-ad-480x214.jpg 480w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 936px, 100vw\" \/><\/p>\n<p>The minimum average daily budget is $15 and the minimum lifetime budget is $250. You can enter a custom amount. Based on the audience, Spotify can predict whether you\u2019ll spend some or all of your budget.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-setup-budget.jpg\" alt=\"spotify advertising - how to run spotify ads - choose budget\" width=\"853\" height=\"598\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-73597\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-setup-budget.jpg 853w, https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-setup-budget-480x337.jpg 480w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 853px, 100vw\" \/><\/p>\n<h3>Step 6: Choose a delivery objective<strong>\u00a0<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p>You can select one of three delivery goals for Spotify to prioritize: impressions, reach, or clicks.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-setup-objective.jpg\" alt=\"spotify advertising - how to run spotify ads - choose objective for ad\" width=\"635\" height=\"599\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-73598\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-setup-objective.jpg 635w, https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-setup-objective-480x453.jpg 480w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 635px, 100vw\" \/><\/p>\n<p>You also get to set the frequency cap (how frequently the ad will appear per day, per week, and per month) and the bid cap.<\/p>\n<p>Spotify offers recommendations for the bid amount based on similar audiences.<\/p>\n<h3>Step 7: Create your ad<\/h3>\n<p>Fill in the ad details like ad name, advertiser name, and tagline, and choose the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/ws\/2022\/04\/13\/call-to-action-examples\">CTA<\/a>. Set the destination URL and tracking URL (optional).<\/p>\n<p>You can see an example of what the ad preview looks like at this stage:<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-setup-ad-details.jpg\" alt=\"spotify advertising - how to run spotify ads - create your add\" width=\"603\" height=\"600\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-73599\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-setup-ad-details.jpg 603w, https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-setup-ad-details-480x478.jpg 480w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 603px, 100vw\" \/><\/p>\n<p>Add a companion image that\u2019ll appear while the ad plays and your logo (optional). These images should be in JPG or PNG format and at least 640 x 640 pixels.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-setup-image-logo.jpg\" alt=\"spotify advertising - how to run spotify ads - add image and logo\" width=\"739\" height=\"600\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-73600\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-setup-image-logo.jpg 739w, https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-setup-image-logo-480x390.jpg 480w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 739px, 100vw\" \/><\/p>\n<p>Here\u2019s what the preview looks like when those images are uploaded:<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-setup-ad-preview.jpg\" alt=\"spotify advertising - how to run spotify ads - ad preview example\" width=\"320\" height=\"600\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-73601\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-setup-ad-preview.jpg 320w, https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-setup-ad-preview-160x300.jpg 160w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 320px) 100vw, 320px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>Since we chose audio as the ad format, we\u2019ll show you the options you have:<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-setup-add-audio.jpg\" alt=\"spotify advertising - how to run spotify ads - add audio for ad\" width=\"604\" height=\"599\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-73602\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-setup-add-audio.jpg 604w, https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-setup-add-audio-480x476.jpg 480w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 604px, 100vw\" \/><\/p>\n<p>The first option is pretty straightforward. You can upload your audio or choose one from the library.<\/p>\n<p>But the \u201cCreate Audio\u201d option is a game-changer for businesses. You don\u2019t even need a script or an in-house voice actor. Spotify can write one for you and produce your ad in 2-4 business days.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-setup-creative-brief.jpg\" alt=\"spotify advertising - how to run spotify ads - creative brief\" width=\"321\" height=\"599\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-73603\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-setup-creative-brief.jpg 321w, https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-setup-creative-brief-161x300.jpg 161w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 321px) 100vw, 321px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>If you choose video as the ad format, you also get the option to enable viewability tracking thanks to third-party vendors along with the optional tracking URL.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-viewability-tracking.jpg\" alt=\"spotify advertising - how to run spotify ads - viewability tracking\" width=\"936\" height=\"491\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-73604\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-viewability-tracking.jpg 936w, https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-viewability-tracking-480x252.jpg 480w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 936px, 100vw\" \/><\/p>\n<p>You can use drag and drop the video to upload the content&#8211;no hidden bells and whistles there.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-setup-upload-video.jpg\" alt=\"spotify advertising - how to run spotify ads - upload video ad\" width=\"936\" height=\"346\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-73605\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-setup-upload-video.jpg 936w, https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-setup-upload-video-480x177.jpg 480w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 936px, 100vw\" \/><\/p>\n<h3>Step 8: Add your business address and payment information<\/h3>\n<p>Once you add this information, you can then submit your ad for approval.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-setup-add-payment.jpg\" alt=\"spotify advertising - how to run spotify ads - add business info and payment info\" width=\"936\" height=\"514\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-73606\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-setup-add-payment.jpg 936w, https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-setup-add-payment-480x264.jpg 480w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 936px, 100vw\" \/><\/p>\n<div id=\"tips\"><\/div>\n<h2>Tips to tune into success with Spotify advertising<\/h2>\n<p>Due to \u201cthe carryover effect,\u201d Spotify listeners are just as engaged while listening to ads as they were while streaming music or binging on podcasts. <a href=\"https:\/\/storage.pardot.com\/52662\/1677552207ZGvhSQfc\/Sonic_Science_US.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">60%<\/a> of the ad engagement is carried over from what listeners consumed before.<\/p>\n<p>In short, you\u2019ve got a highly receptive audience that\u2019s willing to engage with your ad. Apart from the usual advice&#8211;mention your brand, include a <a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/ws\/2021\/10\/05\/best-call-to-action-phrases\">strong CTA<\/a>, and stay on message&#8211;here are some data-backed best practices you may want to use.<\/p>\n<h3>Mix audio, video, and display<\/h3>\n<p>Your best bet at holding your audience\u2019s attention and making it count is to combine different ad formats for your Spotify advertising campaigns.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-ad-recall-chart.jpg\" alt=\"spotify advertising - ad recall for spotify audio and video ads\" width=\"786\" height=\"600\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-73607\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-ad-recall-chart.jpg 786w, https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-ad-recall-chart-480x366.jpg 480w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 786px, 100vw\" \/><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em><a href=\"https:\/\/ads.spotify.com\/en-US\/news-and-insights\/dentsu-research-attention-economy\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Source<\/a><\/em><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/ads.spotify.com\/en-US\/news-and-insights\/dentsu-research-attention-economy\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Dentsu\u2019s study<\/a> has proven that Spotify\u2019s ability to run ads in different formats yields those benchmark-breaking metrics.<\/p>\n<h3>Don\u2019t skimp on the ad creative<\/h3>\n<p>Strong ad creative is the biggest lever you can pull when it comes to making an engaged audience convert. Dentsu\u2019s data showed that a poor creative can cause a <a href=\"https:\/\/ads.spotify.com\/en-US\/news-and-insights\/dentsu-research-attention-economy\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">17%<\/a> decline in ad recall.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-ad-creative-example.jpg\" alt=\"spotify advertising ad creative examples\" width=\"778\" height=\"600\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-73608\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-ad-creative-example.jpg 778w, https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-ad-creative-example-480x370.jpg 480w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 778px, 100vw\" \/><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em><a href=\"https:\/\/ads.spotify.com\/en-IN\/ad-experiences\/sponsored-sessions-specs\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Source<\/a><\/em><\/p>\n<p>Spotify allows you to create compelling ads with free built-in creative tools like background music and 3D audio (AKA the surround sound effect) and deliver them in an engaging format like Homepage Takeover or Overlay.<\/p>\n<h3>Let the genre guide you<\/h3>\n<p>Since audio ads have a 55-70 word range, you have to be economical with your choice of words. You don\u2019t want to sound rushed or breathless, so edit with a heavy hand.<\/p>\n<p>Knowing your audience well can help with that. If you\u2019re going to serve ads to sports fans, you might want to play up the energy and sprinkle in some sports metaphors. But if the goal is to get in front of an audience that prioritizes wellness, you want to adopt a calm, soothing tone. 73% of the Sonic Science study participants were willing to listen to an ad if the tone fits their current activity.<\/p>\n<h3>Write for real people\u2019s ears<\/h3>\n<p>Your priority is to connect with real listeners. Remember not to let rigid brand guidelines eliminate the human element from your script.<\/p>\n<p>Use contractions, colloquialisms, and hang up the grammarian hat for a while. Infuse the script with your personality, a little bit of humor, and bring that main character energy.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe width=\"100%\" height=\"352\" style=\"border-radius: 12px;\" src=\"https:\/\/open.spotify.com\/embed\/track\/3A80zdqVvmCd3fmB6aUToZ?utm_source=generator\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"><\/iframe><\/p>\n<div class='et-box et-shadow'>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class='et-box-content'>\u270d\ufe0f Want more ad copywriting tips? Download our free guide &gt;&gt; <a href=\"https:\/\/marketing.wordstream.com\/WSContentDLWebBlogInContentTextLinkTrickstoClicks.html?cid=Web_Blog_InContent_TextLink_TrickstoClicks_Download\" class=\"waffle-rich-text-link\">10 Tricks to Get the Click: How to Write Exceptional Ad Copy<\/a><\/div><\/div>\n<div id=\"cost\"><\/div>\n<h2>Spotify advertising costs: How much do you have to invest?<\/h2>\n<p>Now that you understand how to run Spotify ads, let\u2019s talk about how much they\u2019re going to cost you.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-ad-spending-audio-channels.jpg\" alt=\"spotify advertising ad spending on audio channels\" width=\"936\" height=\"527\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-73609\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-ad-spending-audio-channels.jpg 936w, https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-ad-spending-audio-channels-480x270.jpg 480w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 936px, 100vw\" \/><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em><a href=\"https:\/\/www.statista.com\/outlook\/amo\/advertising\/audio-advertising\/digital-audio-advertising\/united-states#ad-spending\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Source<\/a><\/em><\/p>\n<p>While you can get started with the minimum daily budget is $15 and a lifetime minimum budget of $250 in the self-serve Ad Studio, here\u2019s how the pricing works for all the models:<\/p>\n<h3>Self-serve<\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Minimum lifetime spend: $250<\/li>\n<li>Free access to background music, voice actors, and professional audio mixing.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>There\u2019s an auction for audio and video ads that are served while listeners stream music. If there\u2019s more competition for your audience, you might have to place a more aggressive bid to effectively spend your budget.<\/p>\n<p>Podcast ads, on the other hand, have fixed prices and aren\u2019t part of the ad auction.<\/p>\n<p>You can watch how the ad auction works <a href=\"https:\/\/youtu.be\/oPzLoHn_h8w\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">here<\/a>.<\/p>\n<h3>Automated<\/h3>\n<p>If you\u2019re working with a DSP (demand-side platform), you can access Spotify inventory through:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Private Marketplaces (PMPs) which have an auction-based model that allows for dynamic bidding, or\u2026<\/li>\n<li>Programmatic Guaranteed (PG) buys that have a fixed rate that you can discuss with a Spotify rep prior to launch.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3>Direct<\/h3>\n<p>If you\u2019re looking to create customized experiences, mix up the ad formats, or want a guaranteed inventory, you can speak to the Spotify team to set rates and campaign parameters. The pricing is based on the format, audience, and any add-ons you choose.<\/p>\n<div id=\"reporting\"><\/div>\n<h2>How to measure Spotify advertising success<\/h2>\n<p>Apart from using Spotify\u2019s <a href=\"https:\/\/newsroom.spotify.com\/2023-06-13\/evolving-brands-measurement-experience-with-all-new-spotify-ad-analytics\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">built-in ad analytics<\/a>, you can work with approved third-party measurement partners to act on real-time insights and make changes to your ad or ad sets.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/measure-spotify-advertising.gif\" alt=\"measure spotify advertising\" width=\"936\" height=\"702\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-73610\" \/><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em><a href=\"https:\/\/ads.spotify.com\/en-US\/news-and-insights\/introducing-spotify-ad-analytics\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Source<\/a><\/em><\/p>\n<p>If you\u2019re using Ad Studio, you\u2019ll see some results on the dashboard in 24 hours. You can see how many people you\u2019ve reached and the frequency with which your ad has been heard.<\/p>\n<p>In the <a href=\"https:\/\/ads.spotify.com\/en-NL\/help-center\/reporting-ad-studio\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">report tab<\/a>, you\u2019ll receive a summary of delivery, performance, and audience insight metrics.<\/p>\n<p>Some key metrics you may want to take note of include:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Impressions<\/li>\n<li>Completion rate<\/li>\n<li>CPM (cost per impression)<\/li>\n<li>CTR (click-through rate)<\/li>\n<li>Ad played to X% (25%, 75%, or 100%)<\/li>\n<li>Genre (what your audience was listening to before the ad played)<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>These reports can easily be exported to your existing measurement tech stack if needed.<\/p>\n<p>If you\u2019re working with Spotify to manage your campaigns, you can tap into the custom measurement solutions on offer. Spotify has partnered with third-party measurement platforms to help you measure viewability and brand lift.<\/p>\n<div class='et-box et-shadow'>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class='et-box-content'>\u2734\ufe0f Free guide! Download it now &gt;&gt; <a href=\"https:\/\/marketing.wordstream.com\/WSContentDLWebBlogInContentTextLinkAllStarPlaybook.html?cid=Web_Blog_InContent_TextLink_AllStarPlaybook_Download\" class=\"waffle-rich-text-link\">The All-Star Online Advertising Playbook<\/a><\/div><\/div>\n<div id=\"examples\"><\/div>\n<h2>Real-life Spotify advertising examples from brands you know<\/h2>\n<p>Thinking about running your first ad on Spotify? Check out these three examples from well-known brands that you can use as inspiration.<\/p>\n<h3>Pizza Hut tempted pizza lovers on game day to order in<\/h3>\n<p>With an audio-first campaign, <a href=\"https:\/\/ads.spotify.com\/en-US\/inspiration\/pizza-hut-ad-studio-case-study\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Pizza Hut<\/a> managed to keep delivery services top of mind for their niche audience segments\u2014families, folks interested in gaming, TV, or sports, and Gen Z. Their immersive audio ad resulted in a CTR of 0.23% from sports enthusiasts and 0.57% from parents and gamers, smashing Spotify\u2019s benchmarks for CTR of 0.06%.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe width=\"476\" height=\"476\" style=\"border: none; overflow: hidden;\" src=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/plugins\/video.php?height=476&amp;href=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FSpotifyAds%2Fvideos%2F663276731338212%2F&amp;show_text=false&amp;width=476&amp;t=0\" scrolling=\"no\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"><\/iframe><\/p>\n<h3>Salesforce cut through the noise to reach millennial business decision-makers<\/h3>\n<p>In an effort to reach millennial B2B buyers during their downtime, <a href=\"https:\/\/ads.spotify.com\/en-US\/inspiration\/salesforce-advertising-campaign\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Salesforce<\/a> ran multi-format campaigns&#8211;a combination of audio, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/ws\/2019\/05\/23\/google-display-ads\">display<\/a>, and video takeover&#8211;across playlists and podcasts that were relevant.<\/p>\n<p>The result? Salesforce boosted brand affinity (+10%), consideration (+11%), and unaided recall (+30%) among business decision-makers.<\/p>\n<h3>Neutrogena connected with health and beauty buyers to promote anti-acne products<\/h3>\n<p>To promote their latest acne-fighting product line, <a href=\"https:\/\/ads.spotify.com\/en-US\/inspiration\/neutrogena-case-study\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Neutrogena<\/a> used Spotify\u2019s first and third-party data to engage with health and beauty product consumers through digital audio and display ads.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-example-neutrogena.jpg\" alt=\"spotify advertising example from neutrogena\" width=\"774\" height=\"599\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-73611\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-example-neutrogena.jpg 774w, https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/spotify-advertising-example-neutrogena-480x371.jpg 480w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 774px, 100vw\" \/><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em><a href=\"https:\/\/ads.spotify.com\/en-US\/inspiration\/neutrogena-case-study\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Source<\/a><\/em><\/p>\n<p>The campaign was a roaring success, with a 12-point increase in <a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/ws\/2015\/07\/10\/brand-awareness\">brand awareness<\/a> and a 13-point increase in intent to purchase the anti-acne products.<\/p>\n<div id=\"faqs\"><\/div>\n<h2>Spotify advertising frequently asked questions<\/h2>\n<p>Still have some questions or want to learn more? Here are some FAQs when it comes to Spotify advertising.<\/p>\n<h3>What Spotify advertising objectives should I choose?<\/h3>\n<p>You can choose to boost awareness (through reach and impressions) or consideration (through clicks) for your product or service. Keep in mind, you can only choose one objective.<\/p>\n<h3>What key metrics for Spotify advertising should I focus on?<\/h3>\n<p>There are four general KPIs you should keep an eye on: impressions, reach, frequency, and audio completion rate. With Spotify\u2019s managed ad services, you can also tap into a custom measurement solution that helps you understand the reach with verification tools, resonance with brand lift studies, and reaction through offline sales and in-store visits.<\/p>\n<h3>How much does it cost to put an ad on Spotify?<\/h3>\n<p>The minimum you have to spend on Spotify is $250. Each model&#8211;self-serve, programmatic, and direct&#8211;have a different pricing structure. While you can see what you\u2019ll end up paying for the self-serve Ad Studio, other models require you to get in touch with their team (or a marketing company that runs Spotify advertising) to get a quote.<\/p>\n<h3>What type of ads does Spotify use?<\/h3>\n<p>Spotify offers a mix of audio and video ads that can be served while listeners stream music or podcasts. Advertisers can also make use of custom experiences to take over the Spotify homepage or sponsor a playlist.<\/p>\n<h2>Is Spotify advertising right for you?<\/h2>\n<p>Now that you have a clear understanding of everything you need to know about Spotify advertising, you can determine whether it\u2019s a good option for your business. As with anything, it might be beneficial to test this advertising platform to see if it can <a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/ws\/2023\/01\/12\/how-to-generate-leads\">drive leads<\/a> and brand awareness for you.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>The comprehensive guide covers everything you need to know about Spotify advertising. From ad types and best practices to cost and examples. <\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":264,"featured_media":73614,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"_et_pb_use_builder":"","_et_pb_old_content":"","_et_gb_content_width":"","om_disable_all_campaigns":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[94],"tags":[],"dipi_cpt_category":[],"class_list":["post-73567","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-lead-generation"],"acf":[],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v25.8 - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\